dfu-util: dfu-util (Device firmware update USB programmer)
dfu-util:
dfu-util: dfu-util is a program that implements the host (PC) side of the
dfu-util: USB DFU (Universal Serial Bus Device Firmware Upgrade) protocol.
dfu-util: In the OpenMoko project (for example), this program is used to
dfu-util: communicate with the specially enhanced u-boot boot loader, which
dfu-util: implements the DFU device side.
dfu-util:
dfu-util: Homepage: http://dfu-util.gnumonks.org
